N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1273.11 - Transfer of bulk fuel within terminal boundaries prohibited

State Regulations

The transfer of bulk aircraft or commercial fuel from one
vehicular tender into another is prohibited within the boundaries of the air
terminal. Notes
